message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $95. I believe it offers excellent value at this price.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of the product. I would like to propose a price of $85 for the product.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I'm willing to come down a bit, how about $90?
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. I would like to counter with an offer of $87 for the product.
